page_id: S4-X-08
title: Repository Settings
platform: Linux
sections:
  - Repository
  - Status
  - Actions
fields:
  - Name
  - Location
  - Type
  - Last opened
  - Core version
  - Access
  - Watcher
  - Cloud
  - Fallback to Inbox
actions:
  reconnect_repository: RepositorySettingsView.ReconnectRepository
  choose_another_folder: RepositorySettingsView.ChooseAnotherFolder
  platform_capabilities: RepositorySettingsView.OpenPlatformCapabilities
  save_fallback_to_inbox: RepositorySettingsView.SaveFallbackToInboxAsync
  export_diagnostics: RepositorySettingsView.ExportDiagnosticsAsync
states:
  loading: Loading repository settings...
  empty: No repository connected.
  failed: Could not load repository status.
safety:
  - The page calls load_config and update_config through LinuxRepositoryCoreBridge for C4-20.
  - The page calls get_platform_capabilities through LinuxRepositoryCoreBridge for C4-17.
  - Export diagnostics writes redacted settings metadata under .areamatrix/generated/diagnostics.
  - Export diagnostics is disabled when repository access capability is not UI-enabled.
  - The page does not expose delete, Trash, rescan, import, or cloud SDK configuration.
